Package: ineqx
Type: Package
Title: Descriptive and Causal Variance Decomposition
Version: 0.3.0
Authors@R: person("Benjamin", "Rosche", role=c("aut", "cre"),
    email="benjamin.rosche@gmail.com", comment=c(ORCID="0000-0001-5196-625X"))
Description: Implements descriptive and causal variance decomposition for
    analyzing within-group and between-group inequality. Decomposes the
    treatment effect on total variance into behavioral, compositional, and
    pre-treatment components. Supports configurable decomposition orderings
    and Shapley values. See Rosche (2025) for methodological details.
